    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "[Ethereum yellow paper](https://ethereum.github.io/yellowpaper/paper.pdf) spells out the removal of all leading zeros in appendix B just below equation 197, and that zero scaler writes as `0x80` is [explicitly tested for](https://github.com/ethereum/tests/blob/develop/RLPTests/rlptest.json#L34) in the ethereum reference tests. and a number of [invalid tests](https://github.com/ethereum/tests/blob/develop/RLPTests/invalidRLPTest.json#L52) flag `0x00` as a scalar length as invalid.",
